SQL_STMT_U.val:
select e.hpp_holdernummer , c.ppr_id , d.ppr_relatienummer , d.ppr_productnummer , d.ppr_volgnr_per_product , f.cl_id from producten a , product_configurator_temp_vw b , producten_per_relatie c , pr_products_per_client_vw d inner join holders_per_product e on e.hpp_relatienummer =d.ppr_relatienummer and e.hpp_product =d.ppr_productnummer and e.hpp_product_volgnr=d.ppr_volgnr_per_product and e.hpp_type_holder =1 and e.hpp_holdernummer >= ~1 and e.hpp_holdernummer <= ~2 inner join clienten f on f.cl_nummer=d.ppr_relatienummer inner join rekeningen_per_product g on g.rpp_productnummer =d.ppr_productnummer and g.rpp_volgnr_per_product=d.ppr_volgnr_per_product and g.rpp_relatienummer =d.ppr_relatienummer and g.rpp_rekeningsoort <999 inner join rekeningen h on h.re_nummer =g.rpp_relatienummer and h.re_rekening =g.rpp_rekening_nummer and h.re_soort =g.rpp_rekeningsoort and h.re_muntsoort =g.rpp_valuta and to_number(substr(nvl(h.re_openingsdatum,'0000'),1,4)) <=~3 where b.pr_id =a.pr_id and b.code = 'IS_BPS_PRODUCT' and b.value = '1' and c.ppr_productnummer=a.pr_productnummer and d.ppr_id =c.ppr_id and d.ppr_status >0 and ( d.ppr_status <9 or (d.ppr_status =9 and to_number(substr(nvl(c.ppr_einddatum,'0000'),1,4)) >=~3) )
order by e.hpp_holdernummer

SQL_STMT_U.val: select * from ( select e.hpp_holdernummer from producten a , product_configurator_temp_vw b , producten_per_relatie c , pr_products_per_client_vw d inner join holders_per_product e on e.hpp_relatienummer =d.ppr_relatienummer and e.hpp_product =d.ppr_productnummer and e.hpp_product_volgnr=d.ppr_volgnr_per_product and e.hpp_type_holder =1 and e.hpp_holdernummer >= ~1 and e.hpp_holdernummer <= ~2 where b.pr_id =a.pr_id and b.code = 'IS_BPS_PRODUCT' and b.value = '1' and c.ppr_productnummer=a.pr_productnummer and d.ppr_id =c.ppr_id and d.ppr_status >0 and ( d.ppr_status <9 or ( d.ppr_status =9 and to_number(substr(nvl(c.ppr_einddatum,'0000'),1,4)) =~3 ) ) order by e.hpp_holdernummer :4 ) where rownum<=1

select * from ( select a.holdernummer from nltaxmnth_detail a inner join nltaxmnth_header b on b.line_id =a.header_line_id and b.collection_year = ~1 and b.collection_month= ~2 where a.holdernummer >= ~3 and a.holdernummer<= ~4 and a.line_type=1 and a.reported=0 order by a.holdernummer :5 ) where rownum<=1

select count( distinct e.hpp_holdernummer) from producten a , product_configurator_temp_vw b , producten_per_relatie c , pr_products_per_client_vw d inner join holders_per_product e on e.hpp_relatienummer =d.ppr_relatienummer and e.hpp_product =d.ppr_productnummer and e.hpp_product_volgnr=d.ppr_volgnr_per_product and e.hpp_type_holder =1 and e.hpp_holdernummer >= ~1 and e.hpp_holdernummer <= ~2 where b.pr_id =a.pr_id and b.code = 'IS_BPS_PRODUCT' and b.value = '1' and c.ppr_productnummer=a.pr_productnummer and d.ppr_id =c.ppr_id and d.ppr_status >0 and ( d.ppr_status <9 or ( d.ppr_status =9 and to_number(substr(nvl(c.ppr_einddatum,'0000'),1,4)) =~3 ) )

select count(distinct a.holdernummer) from nltaxmnth_detail a inner join nltaxmnth_header b on b.line_id =a.header_line_id and b.collection_year = ~1 and b.collection_month= ~2 where a.holdernummer >= ~3 and a.holdernummer<= ~4 and a.line_type=1 and a.reported=0
